he would send me, I think it was $60. A month? A 
month. And I would give my mother, I insisted on

27:09.194 --> 27:18.748
paying and my mother wouldn't think about it, but I 
think I gave my mother $30. And I kept 30 and out of

27:19.538 --> 27:43.880
that 30 we budgeted to buy, you know, clothes and if 
